<plot>An innocent young witness to a brutal crime finds herself hunted by the dangerous men and woman responsible. Her only protection is a hard-boiled police inspector named Lee. Relentlessly pursued by the criminals, the two attempt to take refuge inside an old barn. Lee, heavily outnumbered and out-gunned but determined to protect the witness at all costs, takes a final stand against the horde of gangsters hellbent on silencing her. Justice will be served no matter how much blood must be shed.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?237253</url></doc>
